flowchart LR
  M[message] --> O[orchestrator LM]
  O -->|tool-call| T[retrieve / search_web / visit_webpage]
  T -->|output| O
  O -->|write_code| C[coder LM]
  C -->|tool-call| T
  T -->|output| C
  C -->|code| V[code_validator]
  V -.->|opt-in| Rv[reviewer LM]
  V -->|feedback| C
  Rv -->|feedback| C
  C -->|final code| O
  O -->|response| G{guard<br>malformed?}
  G -->|yes| O
  G -->|no| Resp[response]
